snippet.title: GUILD WARS PROPHECIES - Cinematic Trailer Remastered HD
snippet.description:
This is the remastered version of the Guild Wars Prophecies cinematic trailer, the classic MMO developed by ArenaNet and published by NCSoft in 2005.
